Trump read the article and started asking about Walsh.&quot;
Goldmacher added that then-Chief of Staff Reince Priebus and White House Secretary Rob Porter &quot;were trying to implement a system to manage and document the information that President Trump would receive.&quot;
Would that work?
Now, three months later, Kelly is trying to implement the same strategy.
He may turn out to be a more effective manager than Priebus, but Trump&#39;s impulsiveness won&#39;t go away, and his aides are still vying for power.
These immutable factors will certainly make Kelly&#39;s mission more difficult.
