The state counts on citizens in the defense of the state.
It will support their training.
Financial support for associations useful in the defense of the state, with voluntary shooting training or with a team of training trainers is envisaged by the objective of the act on the readiness of citizens for the defense of the state.
The Ministry of Defense, which was given the task of processing it by the government, hopes that it will increase the physical fitness of the Czechs and their abilities, which the state could then use in crisis situations.
