It was often an intimidating and unpleasant experience, said James Vitrano, Ruby Tuesday&#39;s general manager, who previously said there was no reliable way to track employee complaints.
Now that the company is using Convercent, problems that previously never reached managers sitting in offices, miles away from the actual resolution of complaints - such as discrimination, harassment or unfair treatment - are ensured to be quickly detected and resolved.
